snippet.title: Lorelai - Official Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The little she had was taken away, but Lorelai refuses to give up, she will fight. Even death won't stop her from getting it all back. 

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/593960/Lorelai/

Thanks for your kind comments & reaction to the teaser trailer!

Lorelai by Harvester Games is the 3rd and final game in the Devil Came Through Here trilogy and is expected in the earlier months of 2019. 

Music by Black Casino And The Ghost:
https://blackcasinoandtheghost.bandcamp.com/

#Lorelai #HarvesterGames #TheCatLady
